.SH NAME
xprintidle \- utility printing user's idle time in X
.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B xprintidle
.RI [ OPTION .\|.\|.]
.
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B xprintidle
is a utility that queries the X server for the user's idle time and prints
it to stdout (in milliseconds).
.
